name: Classic Hawaiian
description: Get a Glimpse of the Ancient Hawaii Art
overview: Classic Hawaiiana is a website dedicated to classic moments in the Hawaiian history. Recognized as a line of Distinctive Fine Art Giclee reproductions of Hawaiian artworks, the website offers a massive selection of Hawaiian paintings, prints and photographs. Images of prominent places, eminent Hawaiian figures and other artworks are displayed on the website. Hawaiian art aficionados can choose from an assorted variety of paintings available in black and white, color or sepia tones. The prints feature an antique torn edge effect floated on a variety of fine colored suede matting and finished with a distinctive tropical frame, including the option of adding a white linen liner.
